title: Watch India launch advanced military satellite on rocket's 1st flight since May 2025 failure
description: You can watch India launch 16 payloads, including an advanced military satellite, to space tonight (Jan. 11). It will be the first liftoff of a PSLV rocket since a May 2025 failure.
